207
00:14:36,506 --> 00:14:38,188
Chýba?

208
00:14:38,189 --> 00:14:40,318
- Čo chýba?
- Postav sa.

209
00:14:40,514 --> 00:14:41,277
Čo?

210
00:14:53,288 --> 00:14:54,384
Čo je to?

212
00:15:19,202 --> 00:15:20,260
